Feature: Create customer user address
  In order to to manage addresses for Customer User
  As an administrator
  I want to create new Address

  Scenario: Feature Background
    Given I login as administrator
    And I go to System / Configuration
    And I follow "System Configuration/General Setup/Language Settings" on configuration sidebar
    And I fill form with:
      | Supported Languages | [English, Zulu] |
      | Use Default         | false           |
      | Default Language    | Zulu            |
    And I submit form
    When I go to System / Localization / Translations
    And I click "Update Cache"
    Then I should see "Translation Cache has been updated" flash message

